00:04:48.380 --> 00:04:51.300
She had covered a couple
hundred yards, dropped her cubs.

00:04:51.300 --> 00:04:52.250
- Here take them.

00:04:52.250 --> 00:04:54.800
- And then came by herself
back around behind me.

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:56.420
