00:04:56.420 --> 00:04:58.810
going through the brush,
the grass is flying.

00:04:58.810 --> 00:05:00.680
Pulled my bear spray,
pulled the safety out,

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:02.800
thinking it's probably
just a bluff charge.

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:05.450
But just in case gonna have it ready.

00:05:05.450 --> 00:05:07.860
In that two seconds she had
already covered that distance

00:05:07.860 --> 00:05:09.810
