00:05:25.500 --> 00:05:28.160
no you would feel like the hooker.

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:31.350
Marv Albert used to bite
hookers in the back, didn't he?

00:05:31.350 --> 00:05:32.183
Continue.

00:05:32.183 --> 00:05:34.030
- But five seconds and she was gone.

00:05:34.030 --> 00:05:35.680
And I'm thinking wow, I was lucky,

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:37.490
I just survived a grizzly bear attack.

00:05:37.490 --> 00:05:39.380
And I looked and I got arms bleeding

00:05:39.380 --> 00:05:41.410
and like alright time
to go to the hospital

00:05:41.410 --> 00:05:42.740
and get some stitches.

00:05:42.740 --> 00:05:44.220
So I start down the trail

00:05:44.220 --> 00:05:45.430
and all of a sudden I hear

00:05:45.430 --> 00:05:47.080
just something behind me makes me turn

00:05:47.080 --> 00:05:48.440
and that bear had come off the ridge

00:05:48.440 --> 00:05:50.300
and she's like 10 feet behind me now

00:05:50.300 --> 00:05:52.700
and she's coming wide
open again in a charge.

00:05:52.700 --> 00:05:54.880
And there was no time, I
had bear spray in my hand,

00:05:54.880 --> 00:05:56.450
pistol here, no time to even turn,

00:05:56.450 --> 00:05:57.830
I just protect my vitals--

00:05:57.830 --> 00:05:59.580
- By the way I don't even
know what vitals are.

00:05:59.580 --> 00:06:00.860
Okay so what is that?

00:06:00.860 --> 00:06:02.500
- Just the soft part of your stomach

00:06:02.500 --> 00:06:04.130
that they can tear into--

00:06:04.130 --> 00:06:05.290
- Your neck is a bad spot.

00:06:05.290 --> 00:06:07.260
- The neck could be bad,
they could just one swipe.

00:06:07.260 --> 00:06:08.710
This time she's really mad.

00:06:08.710 --> 00:06:10.710
The first bite was in my left arm

00:06:10.710 --> 00:06:12.300
and I heard the crunch of the bone

00:06:12.300 --> 00:06:13.540
where she broke my arm.

00:06:13.540 --> 00:06:15.524
- [Daniel] I mean I can
see a dip in your arm.

00:06:15.524 --> 00:06:16.357
- There's a big divot there

00:06:16.357 --> 00:06:17.550
that's where the tendons
were sticking out.

00:06:17.550 --> 00:06:18.990
She ripped two tendons loose,

00:06:18.990 --> 00:06:20.170
this whole part of my forearm

00:06:20.170 --> 00:06:21.890
was just kind of shredded from the teeth.

00:06:21.890 --> 00:06:22.840
So I just told myself,

00:06:22.840 --> 00:06:25.340
I'm like you gotta play
dead, you have to hold still

00:06:25.340 --> 00:06:28.160
