00:06:32.850 --> 00:06:34.920
just a little bit of mild pressure.

00:06:34.920 --> 00:06:36.470
I'm just squirming.

00:06:36.470 --> 00:06:38.630
- It's amazing what your body can do

00:06:38.630 --> 00:06:40.160
when you're in a survival situation.

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:41.680
