then the bear just stops.

00:07:03.380 --> 00:07:05.940
And she just kind of
sniffing the back of my neck

00:07:05.940 --> 00:07:07.870
and that was the eeriest
part of the whole thing

00:07:07.870 --> 00:07:10.450
is to actually feel and hear her breath

00:07:10.450 --> 00:07:11.710
right on the back of my neck.

00:07:11.710 --> 00:07:13.560
Just sittin' there going oh
please leave, please leave,

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:15.470
don't move, trying to hold my breath,

00:07:15.470 --> 00:07:17.990
and then she just stood there
for like 30 seconds not moving

00:07:17.990 --> 00:07:20.340
and I'm guessing she's
kinda looking around

00:07:20.340 --> 00:07:22.150
and I'm just like, try not to breath,

00:07:22.150 --> 00:07:23.670
trying to not make a sound.

00:07:23.670 --> 00:07:26.183
And all of a sudden she just
stepped off and disappeared.

00:07:27.150 --> 00:07:28.400
